    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Rowling's Readers</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Donna T Wilson opposes call in July 23 article for establishment of best-seller list for children's books in order to remove Harry Potter books from main best-seller list (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I want to state my opinion about the establishment of a best-seller list for children's books (July 23): I disagree that it should be established in order to remove the Harry Potter books from the main best-seller list. I know many adults who have read all the Harry Potter books, including myself. These books are not just for children, and they deserve to be on the main list.</p>
        <p>Donna T. Wilson  Hurst, Tex.</p>
      </block>
